    {
      "id": "3364750c-f3ba-8006-9d4c-eb1891876f65",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Automatic scoring often uses ML to generate a score but often ignore how well the answer maps to the original question. Authors’ approach identifies cognitive difficiencies and subsequently makes recommendations for remediation. Authors present a case study of their system.",
